name: Titillating Tempest Bob-cap
description:
Our ode to mischievous marauders presupposing the Whethermen's Union, we've combined the warmest knitted goods made in the United States with playful snowflakes and our mission statement boiled down to one word: MISCHIEF! Available in extremely limited quantities, once they're gone-- they're gone. 

Royal Blue Body
Winter White Font 
Charcoal Grey Highlights
Royal Blue, Winter White, and Charcoal Grey Pom
